column3: Can you access the internet any time you want to?
In general, I usually do as I am told
In school, my friends find me aggressive
I am often by myself in school

I am cautious in every new thing that I do
Other children are treated better than me
Children think that I am not intelligent enough
I like dangerous and risky activities
I do exciting, fun activities, and I dont care of the danger
I engage in the following risky offline activities

Mostly a bit true for me
